<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,303,753,779]" pageId="106" pageNumber="107">Remarks</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="106.[189,1398,800,862]" pageId="106" pageNumber="107">
Monotypic. Closely related to 
<taxonomicName box="[546,712,800,826]" class="Laboulbeniomycetes" family="Laboulbeniaceae" genus="Chitonomyces" kingdom="Fungi" order="Laboulbeniales" pageId="106" pageNumber="107" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[546,712,800,826]" italics="true" pageId="106" pageNumber="107">Chitonomyces</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from which it can be separated by the perithecial wall cell arrangement and appendage characteristics.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
